        which is a percentage of the Initial Reversionary Value
      </li>
      <li><b>Percentage of Adjusted Reversionary Value</b> - a variable amount
        which is a percentage of the Adjusted Reversionary Value
      </li>
      <li>
        <b>Percentage of Net Reversionary Value</b> - a variable amount which
        is a percentage of the Net Reversionary Value
      </li>
    </ol>
